## CHANGELOG

### v3.0.3 - 03/11/15
  - Updated Accordion Pro JS to v2.0.2

### v3.0.2 - 03/09/15
  - Minor bug fix (wrt. base64_encode)

### v3.0.1 - 27/08/15
  - Updated Accordion Pro JS to v2.0.1

### v3.0.0 - 26/08/2015
  - Implemented Accordion Pro JS v2
    - Colour schemes
    - Colour styles
    - Tab settings
      - Size
      - Font size
      - Font family
      - Tab icon
    - Panel settings
      - Scrollable (w/ customised scrollbars)
  - Copy shortcode/template tag to clipboard
  - Clone accordion
  - Custom colours and icons for each individual tab
    - Colour picker for custom tab colour
    - Image selector for custom tab icon
  - NB: *DEACTIVATE AND DELETE THE OLD PLUGIN BEFORE UPDATING TO v3!*

### v2.1.0 - 21/05/2015
  - Fixed bug introduced in WP4 (tabbing between visual and text editors)
  - Implemented TinyMCE Advanced support
  - Added option to enable auto formatting of slides

### v2.0.0 - 25/09/2013
  - Responsive
  - Touch support
  - CSS3 animations
  - Vertical accordions
  - *Tons* of other stuff

### v1.1.0 - 10/09/2012
  - Introduced shortcode support
    - NB: embedded shortcodes must be executable outside of 'the loop' to work, some plugins don't support this
  - Fixed Chrome animation artifacts bug
  - Fixed FF15 stitch theme bug

### v1.0.1 - 06/02/12
  - Added 'wmode' to list of permitted attributes

### v1.0.0 - 04/02/12
  - Initial release